# Same machine: use localhost. If connection hangs, use the instance port instead of name (no Browser needed):
# In SQL Server Configuration Manager → MSSQL2025 → TCP/IP → IP Addresses → IPAll → TCP Port (or TCP Dynamic Ports).
# Named instance: Server=localhost\MSSQL2025
# By port (replace 49152 with your instance port): Server=localhost,49152
